items.title: Project
items.content_html:
Modelling

Developing

Start a development server:

bash
# http://127.0.0.1:5173
pnpm dev

or listen to different IP and port:

bash
# http://127.0.0.1:3000
pnpm dev --port 3000
# http://0.0.0.0:3000
nr dev --host 0.0.0.0 --port 3000

Building

Create a production version of ur blog:

bash
pnpm build
